        Access Basic FAQ for comp.databases.ms-access, version .01

This is the first stab at an evolving Access BASIC FAQ list. There's
two ways I can approach this. I can gather tons of questions and
answers together and format them neatly and then post the FAQ, or I
can develop the FAQ on-line by posting every version and soliciting
help from the newsgroup readers. I am planning on using the second
method. If you object, email me. If you object strongly, killfile me.

This FAQ will generally be focused on Access BASIC, as opposed to SQL,
and other advanced Access topics, since this is my area of
expertise. Any contributions concerning SQL and other Access features
will be included (probably) but won't get as much of my attention. 

The draft FAQ list is divided into two sections. (These may be posted
seperately in the future). 

The first section contains questions for which I don't have a
"definitive" answer. I'm asking all interested readers to contribute
answers to these questions, either by email if you're shy, or by
followup. When a consensus emerges among the group of contributors
I'll move the question and it's new answer to the second section of
the FAQ. You are all asked to contribute both questions and answers.

The second section then, contains questions and answers in the usual
FAQ format. Anyone is welcome to provide commentary or argument
concerning the answers in this section.

Eventually I'll impose some order on the individual sections
(i.e. Beginner's Questions, Net Resurce Questions, etc.), but for now
I'll just lump it all together until more questions arrive. Each
question starts with a -*-.

